  <note reference-line="4" id="0">
    <original>ādhipaccasaṃvattanikaṃ (?)</original>
    <type>auto</type>
    <snippet> Atthi arahato puññūpacayoti? Āmantā. Arahā puññābhisaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharoti, āneñjābhisaṅkhāraṃ abhisaṅkharoti, gatisaṃvattaniyaṃ kammaṃ karoti, bhavasaṃvattaniyaṃ kammaṃ karoti, issariyasaṃvattaniyaṃ kammaṃ karoti, adhipaccasaṃvattaniyaṃ </snippet>
